{"tid":876212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港珠澳通車】金巴司機疑「揸錯車」 乘客搭去澳門變珠海：個人呆咗","createTime":"2018-10-25T12:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T13:16:12.000Z","uid":117200,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d31b30a1d2791920ce442649489fc998d426bfd0","tid":876212,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋昨日（24日）通車，來往各口岸的「金巴」穿梭巴士「港珠線」及「港澳線」亦開始營運，《蘋果》接獲市民黎小姐投訴，指今午乘坐12時半出發「港澳線」巴士，車程原定約40分鐘，但疑因司機沒有港澳車牌、只得中港車牌但「揸錯車」，將全車乘客接載至珠海口岸，到埗後更一度要求乘客下車，自行由珠海到澳門，經協調才交另一司機、開另一輛「金巴」接載乘客到澳門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540459503_0f61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540459503_0f61.jpg&h=6b8b688f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎小姐今午第一次乘坐日間票價65元的「金巴」，打算到澳門探望朋友，但就遇上司機疑似「上錯車」。她表示，巴士駛至旅程中後段時，已有乘客陸續發現駛向了珠海方向，有人向司機查詢，但未獲正面回覆，最終巴士在珠海口岸停泊，司機表示無法接載乘客到澳門，一度要求乘客自行由珠海轉車到澳門，黎小姐直言當時「好無奈，成個人呆咗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540459503_f87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540459503_f87b.jpg&h=908f2975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乘客對此不滿鼓譟，該名司機下車跟珠海口岸職員商討後，才安排了另一輛「金巴」及另一名司機，將受影響乘客由珠海口岸送至澳門，最終全車乘客在2時多才到達澳門口岸，較原定時間遲了約1小時。黎小姐指出，一眾乘客按指示登車，懷疑是有關司機「揸錯車」，「我哋喺現場聽到司機同職員對話，估計係司機只得中港車牌，無港澳車牌，所以根本揸唔到去澳門。」"},{"pid":"f53cd0aff12693995b0cb2adb4676feb81fed5c3","tid":876212,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"條路單丫<br />\n點由珠海&lt;&gt;澳門 (新線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"5979912426433275992a6cb737c4febfffc94d9b","tid":876212,"uid":32342,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"上錯車 如離開了澳門的高速路"},{"pid":"f2c4a429acac780baf51e0c3b32efcdf6c32990f","tid":876212,"uid":71748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"珠海同澳門口岸唔係響同一個島？"},{"pid":"deb0990a06f0be9698560b3003c524c2b34f0246","tid":876212,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔可以入境珠海再出境再入境澳門咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正都喺隔離<br />\n好過又再等多成粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:唔知咁樣得唔得"},{"pid":"bfd1c0a5014ab8b40f6f75b373871254efe130cb","tid":876212,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/211527_3c0fa8a2a8f93e82560405ce739f12cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F211527_3c0fa8a2a8f93e82560405ce739f12cb.png&h=94199e52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/211531_eed71f89ca1aa8a8201088c078c9d427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F211531_eed71f89ca1aa8a8201088c078c9d427.png&h=031b6af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講google map<br />\n高德都未有條路資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}